                           <q xml:lang="en">[Fol. 130rb]: This book may not be taken out except (wrapped in) a vestment; this is forbidden by the authority of Peter and Paul. Do not forget me, the community of Däbrä Bǝrhan Giyorgis.</q>
                           
                        </item>
